item.title: [718] Help!
item.dc:creator: @sk8rdude461 sk8rdude461
item.description:
@sk8rdude461 wrote:

iownedyouhard:

Can anyone help me on 718 servers please im new and i need a person who can teach me or tell me what to do! Much appreciated! you can add me on skype

If you need help you need to post what you need help with - that’s what this section is for.

It’s not made for people to get new skype contacts and get help on there. The idea is you first search around the net for your question, if you can’t find an answer, you post here asking for help with the issue. Then if/when we can help you, the answer is now available online for anyone else who has a similar issue as you did, and they can now find the answer easier as your post will be on google.
